{"id":"FUYINGYINGHUA1","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"mode":1,"sequence":[["<size=51>……正直、実感が少し湧かないんだ<\/size>",1],["<size=51>「聖域」を求めて鏡面海域に迷い込んで、翔鶴姉と危ない目に遭って<\/size>",3],["<size=51>そして三笠大先輩と出会って、長門様を目覚めさせて、<\/size>",5],["<size=51>なのにまた、赤城先輩と加賀先輩のいる、この海に踏み込んだなんて<\/size> ",7],["<size=51>赤城先輩たちは一体、何を狙っているの？<\/size>",9],["<size=51>私も、翔鶴姉も、大先輩や長門様でも…ましてや重桜の皆ですらも、それはわからない気がする<\/size>",11],["<size=51>だから、私は――<\/size>",13]]},{"stopbgm":true,"blackBg":true,"sequence":[["",2]],"mode":1,"effects":[{"name":"logo_sakura","active":true}]},{"bgmDelay":1,"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1.5,"black":true,"dur":0.5},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":0.5},"say":"重桜・祭儀（さいぎ）の島","bgm":"xinnong-1","side":2,"effects":[{"name":"logo_sakura","active":false}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","side":2,"dir":1,"dialogShake":{"number":2,"x":8.5,"speed":0.09},"say":"カランカラン！","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","dir":1,"say":"龍鳳さんどいて――！","nameColor":"#a9f548","action":[{"y":30,"x":0,"dur":0.15,"delay":0,"number":2,"type":"shake"}],"side":2,"expression":8,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301100,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"機材を運んでいる特型駆逐艦「響」はバランスを崩して今にも転びそうだ。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","side":2,"dir":1,"dialogShake":{"number":2,"x":8.5,"speed":0.09},"say":"カラン！ドン！カン！","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","side":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"――狼狽しながらも尻もちをついた響は、式典に使われる機材を散らかしてしまった。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg1","dir":1,"say":"あいたた……","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":5,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301100,"typewriter":{"sp